message: Hey, nice to meet you! I see you wanted to go watch Toby Keith!
Are you interested in going? I'm planning to buy tickets soon! Wanna do it!
Sure! Which special are you interested in?
Probably the special that is the cheapest.
What's your favorite Kanye West song?
Probably Runaway or Family Business! Yours?
My favorites are probably We Dont Care and POWER!
